msgid ""
"Solar activity monitor for radio amateurs.\n"
"Provides quick access to solar indices, HF band conditions and VHF "
"propagation via a virtual interface accessible with a screen reader."
msgstr ""
"Solar activity monitor for radio amateurs.\n"
"Provides quick access to solar indices, HF band conditions and VHF "
"propagation via a virtual interface accessible with a screen reader."

